{"entries": [{"source": "https://www.jefftk.com/news.rss", "link": "https://www.jefftk.com/p/opening-facebook-links-externally", "title": "Opening Facebook Links Externally", "date_published": "2023-01-04 08:00:00+00:00", "description": "<p><span>\n\nWhen I'm on my phone and click a link in Facebook I want it to open in\nmy normal browser, but it defaults to an \"in-app\" browser.  I\nreally don't like in-app browsers, and I think </span>\n\n<a href=\"https://infrequently.org/2021/07/hobsons-browser/\">Alex\nRussell's explanation</a> of their problems is very good.  I've turned\nthis behavior off, but Facebook regularly forgets my decision, most\nrecently a few weeks ago.  The setting had moved since \n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/p/selecting-the-default-browser-in-facebook-on-android\">the\nlast time I did this</a>, so here are screenshots showing how to turn\nit off on Android:\n\n\n\n<p>\n\nClick on the icon of your profile image overlaid with a hamburger menu\nin the upper right, and scroll to the bottom:\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-1-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-1.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\nClick \"Settings &amp; privacy\":\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-2-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-2.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\nClick \"Settings\":\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-3-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-3.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\nClick \"Profile settings\":\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-4-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-4.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\nClick \"Media and contacts\" settings:\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-5-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-5.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\nToggle \"Links open externally\":\n\n</p>\n\n<p>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-6-big.jpg\"><img class=\"mobile-fullwidth\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://www.jefftk.com/fb-noiab-6.jpg\" width=\"550\" /><div class=\"image-vertical-spacer\"></div></a>\n\n  </p>", "persistent": false, "language": "en-US", "user": null}], "source": {"url": "https://www.jefftk.com/news.rss", "title": "Jeff Kaufmann"}}